data.description: Welcome home to Valley Church Rd! This home is nestled in a quiet neighborhood in beautiful Weyers Cave, perfectly situated between Staunton and Harrisonburg, and just minutes from the I-81 exit. If you work in the city but prefer rural living, this is the perfect place for you! Inside this split bedroom, ranch-style home, you will find a spacious living room that opens to the large, eat-in kitchen and leads out onto the back deck, perfect for cooking out and entertaining. The side entrance to the home conveniently opens into the large laundry/mud room. The full, unfinished basement presents the perfect possibility for future living space, if wanted. Schedule your personal tour today!
